             were indicted for <rs id="t17821204-39-off192" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17821204-39-off192" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17821204-39-off192" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17821204-39-cd193" type="crimeDate">29th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821204-39-off192 t17821204-39-cd193"></join> last, one iron shovel, value 1 s. 6 d. one pick axe, value 1 s. 6 d. one iron saw, value 1 s. 6 d. the goods and chattels of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17821204-39-victim449" type="victimName">
